title: Cozy Tea in Five Points
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Indian, Take-out, British, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Half the menu is vegan and vegetarian. Has over 60 varieties of loose leaf tea. Indian tea service is vegan (pot chai tea, 2 vegetable samosas & fruit). Vegetable & lentil pie is vegan as well as some soups. Has no vegan desserts. Evening menu is pre-fixe Indian cuisine only with over 50% vegan items.
